headline: LyondellBasell: Post Buy Call Analysis - Lessons In Cyclical Timing And Dividend Sustainability
summary: LyondellBasell (LYB) is downgraded from Buy to Hold after a failed contrarian call and a 22% share price decline since May 2025.
